{"tid":2497036,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"胡錫進洩「弄到輝瑞」急刪文","createTime":"2021-04-20T08:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T08:42:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"01effe671f7cb6c36b6ebf646ebd43162c8d2f78","tid":2497036,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:41:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210420/6YX2BN2RNBHSLFKV4N5P3Z4EQU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210420%2F6YX2BN2RNBHSLFKV4N5P3Z4EQU%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ39Z9R%2B5WvgLevJIGZbvuGo%3D&h=778f572c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210420%2F6YX2BN2RNBHSLFKV4N5P3Z4EQU%2F&h=2f8c8757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210420/6YX2BN2RNBHSLFKV4N5P3Z4EQU/</a><br />\n<br />\n胡錫進洩「弄到輝瑞」急刪文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Md7j7X284mctJAiSXEPwR-np8T0=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PBRO625BJRCOZG6Y4GXKQTN4OU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMd7j7X284mctJAiSXEPwR-np8T0%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPBRO625BJRCOZG6Y4GXKQTN4OU.jpg&h=0c28f681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■胡錫進在微博上載完成接種疫苗的記錄。<br />\n<br />\n內地「大躍進式」推廣打COVID-19疫苗，官媒《環球時報》總編胡錫進亦不遺餘力宣傳，惟他早前在微博發文表示已接種國產疫苗時，卻意外「洩露天機」，提到有人可「幫我搞到輝瑞的接種」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱俊臉怕面癱<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進上周五（16日）在微博表示，他已接種國藥疫苗，兩針相隔28日，沒有不適感覺；他更強調注射後，第二日即可做掌上壓。不過，胡又進一步透露：「在接種疫苗之前，有人表示能幫我搞到輝瑞的接種，我說算了吧，萬一不走運，趕上報道說的小比例面癱，那怎麼辦，我這麼俊的臉，哈哈，保險起見，還是選擇國藥疫苗的啦。」<br />\n<br />\n該帖文隨即惹來網民熱議，有人質疑是否胡以上的官方高層，才有資格接種進口的輝瑞疫苗。胡其後雖然刪帖，但網民已截圖，繼續討論：「為甚麼有人能幫你搞到輝瑞的疫苗？這是在赤裸裸的炫耀特權嗎？」「老胡刪帖，是怕害了30天前就能搞到輝瑞的朋友，用心良苦。」<br />\n<br />\n此前中國為民眾接種的疫苗均為國產。其中科興疫苗臨床數據顯示，有效率為50.4%，僅僅符合世衞50%最低標準。同為國產的國藥及康希諾疫苗，則均未有完整及經醫學界確認的第三期臨床報告。由美國輝瑞和德國BioNTech藥廠合作研究的輝瑞疫苗，有效率為90%以上。惟內地民眾並無渠道在國內接種進口疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n新頭殼"},{"pid":"79d50ffc14bc2e64cea15fffd32b3f6c6d51bbc6","tid":2497036,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:42:44.000Z","msg":"俊臉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screen20Shot202015-09-2720at203.30.3820pm_sTbGV_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreen20Shot202015-09-2720at203.30.3820pm_sTbGV_1200x0.png&h=da684067&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}